## ğŸ“¦ Optional: Run in Docker

### Create a Dockerfile

```Dockerfile
FROM python:3.11-slim
WORKDIR /app
COPY requirements.txt .
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt
COPY webcrawler.py .
CMD ["python", "webcrawler.py"]
```

### Build & Run

```bash
docker build -t link-checker .
docker run -it link-checker
```

